Name: TypeOfRequirementsAssessment
Description: Identifies the type of requirement being assessed such as staffing, funding, source materials, etc. Supports the use of an external controlled vocabulary.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the Requirements Assessment. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: IsSatisfied
Description: A boolean statement of whether the requirement was satisfied or not. A value of "true" indicates that the minimum requirement was satisfied. Note any specific information in the Description.
